page_content: The page discusses upcoming courses and events related to vocational training.
The page is for submitting reporting documents related to foundations or pension institutions.
The page provides information about VWBZ, an organization focused on vocational training in Central Switzerland.
The page lists the board members of VWBZ and their affiliations.
The page provides documents for vocational training preparation and follow-up activities.
The page discusses the mandatory use of an Extranet system for vocational training starting 2023.
The page is focused on colorectal cancer prevention and offers information on screening programs.
The page discusses Prozesseinheiten (PE) and Arbeits- und Lernsituationen (ALS) in vocational training, including the use of rALS software for evaluations.
The page discusses higher vocational education and its increasing importance, particularly in public administration.
The page serves as a portal for vocational training in public administration, offering various resources and information.
